quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  27,77,Aur yeh quran eman walon kay liye yaqeenan hidayat aur rehmat hai
  27,78,Aap ka rab unn kay darmiyan apnay hukum say sab faislay ker dey ga woh bara hi ghalib aur dana hai
  27,79,Pus aap yaqeenan Allah hi per bharosa rakhiye yaqeenan aap sachay aur khullay deen per hain
  27,80,Be-shak aap murdon ko nahi suna saktay hain aur na behron ko apni pukar suna saktay hain jabkay woh peeth pheray roo gardaan ja rahey hon
  27,81,Aur na aap andhon ko unn ki gumrahee say hata ker rehnumaee ker saktay hain aap to sirf unhen suna saktay hain jo humari aayaton per eman laye hain phir woh farmanbardaar ho jatay hain
  27,82,Jab unn kay upper azab ka wada sabit hojaye ga hum zamin say unn kay liye aik janwar nikalen gay jo unn say batein kerta hoga kay log humari aayaton per yaqeen nahi kertay thay
  27,83,Aur jiss din her ummat mein say unn logon kay giroh ko jo humari aayaton ko jhutlatay thay gher ghaar ker layen gay phir woh sab kay sab alaga ker diye jayen gay
  27,84,Jab sab kay sab aa phonchen gay to Allah Taalaa farmaye ga kay tum ney meri aayaton ko bawajood yeh kay tumhen unn ka poora ilm na tha kiyon jhutlaya? Aur yeh bhi batlao kay tum kiya kuch kertay rahey
  27,85,Ba-sabab iss kay kay unhon ney zulm kiya tha unn per baat jum jayegi aur woh kuch na bol saken gay
  27,86,Kiya woh dekh nahi rahey hain kay hum ney raat ko iss liye banaya hai kay woh iss mein aaram hasil kerlen aur din ko hum ney dikhlaney wala banaya hai yaqeenan iss mein unn logon kay liye nishaniyan hain jo emaan-o-yaqeen rakhtay hain
  27,87,Jiss din soor phooka jayega tum sab kay sab aasmanon walay aur zmain walay ghabra uthen gay magar jissay Allah Taalaa chahaye aur saray kay saray aajiz-o-pust ho ker uss kay samney hazir hongay
  27,88,Aur aap paharon ko dekh ker apni jagah jamay huye khayal kertay hain lekin woh bhi badal ki tarah urtay phiren gay yeh hai sanâ€™at Allah ki jiss ney her cheez ko mazboot banaya hai jo kuch tum kertay ho uss say woh ba-khabar hai